#. Description of the theme
#: style.css
#, gp-priority: high
msgid "A Business theme which is ideal for creating a corporate / business website. Appointment Red theme is a child theme of Appointment theme and is the Red color variation. The theme has several extra templates that make it even more powerful and it supports various locales."
msgstr "非常适合创建公司/企业站点的商业主题。Appointment Red主题是Appointment子主题，由红色为主。该主题有几个额外的模板，使其更强大，它支持各种语言环境。"

